text:
Coralee you are correct about MBA classes being canceled. Note Undergrad classes are not. The add/drop deadline is a BYU overall deadline unfortunately the MBA program can’t change the deadline. At least that was what was told to me when I asked professors originally. 

The best thing to do unfortunately is networking with people that have taken the classes and professors try to determine if the class is of interest to you from that.
